 "excerpt": "Sometimes a dish crosses your path that changes your world. This banana ice cream is one of the tastiest desserts I've ever eaten in my life. It's unbelievable! It's soft and creamy! YOU'LL NEED: 6 bananas 125 ml peanut butter NOW: Cut the bananas into thin rounds. Place it on a baking tray and …",
