 "html": "<p>Sometimes a dish crosses your path that changes your world.  This banana ice cream is one of the tastiest desserts I've ever eaten in my life.  It's unbelievable! It's soft and creamy!<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-0291.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1358\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 029\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-0291-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>YOU'LL NEED:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>6 bananas<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1348\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>125 ml peanut butter<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1352\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 023\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-023-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOW:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Cut the bananas into thin rounds. <a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-008.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1349\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 008\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-008-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Place it on a baking tray and cover with cling wrap.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1350\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-018-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Freeze it.</li>\n<li>Put it in your food processor and chop finely.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1351\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 019\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-019-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Mix in the peanut butter.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-024.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1353\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-024-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>It's the tastiest treat in TastyLand!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-027.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1354\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 027\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-027-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>"
}
